==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Antiquary
<hw>An"ti*qua*ry</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Antiquaries</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <def>One devoted to the
study of ancient times through their relics, as inscriptions, monuments,
remains of ancient habitations, statues, coins, manuscripts, etc.; one
who searches for and studies the relics of antiquity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Antiquate</ent>⟦br⟧
